# Sentinel — World Awareness Engine

A real-time geospatial intelligence system ingesting open-source live data streams (ADS-B aircraft, satellite TLEs, earthquakes, weather, AIS marine) and transforming them into structured, queryable, anomaly-detecting intelligence.

## Architecture

```
OSINT Sources → Ingestion → NATS JetStream → Processing Pipeline → TimescaleDB/Redis → API/WebSocket
                                                    ↓
                                              Event Bus (anomalies, geofence, lifecycle)
```

**6 Layers**: Ingestion · Stream Processing · Storage · Analytics · API · Frontend

**Key Systems**: Entity lifecycle state machine · Kalman-based track stitching · Backpressure control · Prometheus observability · Entity-type-aware anomaly detection · First-class event layer

## Quick Start

```bash
# 1. Start infrastructure
docker compose up -d nats timescaledb redis

# 2. Install dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# 3. Copy environment config
cp .env.example .env

# 4. Run the engine
python -m sentinel

# 5. Open API docs
open http://localhost:8000/docs
```

## Data Sources

| Source | Type | Protocol | Update Rate |
|--------|------|----------|-------------|
| OpenSky Network | Aircraft (ADS-B) | REST | 10s |
| USGS | Earthquakes | REST/GeoJSON | 60s |
| CelesTrak | Satellites (TLE+SGP4) | REST | 1hr |
| aisstream.io | Marine Vessels (AIS) | WebSocket | Real-time |
| Open-Meteo | Weather | REST | 5min |

## API Endpoints

| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `/health` | GET | Liveness probe |
| `/ready` | GET | Readiness probe (checks NATS, DB, Redis) |
| `/metrics` | GET | Prometheus metrics |
| `/api/v1/entities` | GET | Query entities (bbox, type, time filters) |
| `/api/v1/entities/{id}/track` | GET | Entity track history |
| `/api/v1/entities/live` | GET | Live entities from Redis cache |
| `/api/v1/events` | GET | Query events (type, severity, time) |
| `/api/v1/geofences` | GET/POST | Geofence CRUD |
| `/api/v1/ws/entities` | WS | Live entity stream |
| `/api/v1/ws/events` | WS | Real-time event stream |

## Testing

```bash
# Unit tests
python -m pytest tests/unit/ -v

# Integration tests (requires Docker services)
docker compose up -d
python -m pytest tests/integration/ -v

# Coverage
python -m pytest tests/ --cov=sentinel --cov-report=term-missing
```

## Tech Stack

- **Python 3.12+** — asyncio-based unified stack
- **NATS JetStream** — message bus with backpressure
- **TimescaleDB + PostGIS** — time-series + geospatial storage
- **Redis 7** — hot state cache with geo-indexing
- **FastAPI** — async REST + WebSocket API
- **Prometheus + structlog** — observability

